{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/tabifier-action/","result":{"data":{"site":{"id":"Site","siteMetadata":{"title":"Ayan's Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"471a396e-3e1d-5ee3-b110-d6e0b3db7306","excerpt":"Want to work at Piep Piper? üë®‚Äçüíª üë©‚Äçüíª\nYou must use this action in all of your repository! My Workflow This action converts leading whitespaces in your‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Want to work at Piep Piper? üë®‚Äçüíª üë©‚Äçüíª\nYou must use this action in all of your repository!</p>\n<h3>My Workflow</h3>\n<p>This action converts leading whitespaces in your repository to tabs. Richard Hendricks will be happy!</p>\n<p>This action takes 1 optional input - <code class=\"language-text\">tabLength</code> (default value is 4 - means 4\nspaces will be replaced by 1 tab. The values are always rounded up, <em>e.g.</em> 7\nspaces will be replaced by 2 tabs). Note that, files inside <code class=\"language-text\">.github</code> directory\nare ignored. Along with this, you also need to specify the <code class=\"language-text\">github_token</code> environment variable.</p>\n<p>Here is an example workflow:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Tabify\n\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">push</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">branches</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span> master <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">jobs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">build</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">runs-on</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ubuntu<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>latest\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">steps</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Repo checkout\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">uses</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> actions/checkout@v2\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Tabify\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">uses</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> ayan<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>b/tabifier<span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>action@master\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">env</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">github_token</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> $<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">with</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token key atrule\">tabLength</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> <span class=\"token key atrule\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Commit and push\n      <span class=\"token key atrule\">run</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">|</span><span class=\"token scalar string\">\n        git status\n        git add .\n        git config --global user.name \"github-actions[bot]\"\n        git config --global user.email \"41898282+github-actions[bot]@users.noreply.github.com\"\n        git commit -m \"Tabify\"\n        # change the link according to your repository\n        git push https://ayan-b:${GITHUB_TOKEN}@github.com/ayan-b/tabifier-playground HEAD:master</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Submission Category:</h3>\n<p>Wacky Wildcards</p>\n<h3>Link to Code</h3>\n<p>The action can be found in this repo: <a href=\"https://github.com/ayan-b/tabifier-action\">tabifier-action</a>.</p>\n<h3>Additional Resources / Info</h3>\n<p>You can see this action in action <a href=\"https://github.com/ayan-b/tabifier-playground\">here</a>.</p>\n<p>Jump responsibly!</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 433px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/405ad2774c91e0a47bc409c08ba5dcba/3561e/Richard-Jumping.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 67.2055427251732%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Richard Jumping\"\n        title=\"Richard Jumping\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/405ad2774c91e0a47bc409c08ba5dcba/3561e/Richard-Jumping.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/405ad2774c91e0a47bc409c08ba5dcba/a80bd/Richard-Jumping.jpg 148w,\n/blog/static/405ad2774c91e0a47bc409c08ba5dcba/1c91a/Richard-Jumping.jpg 295w,\n/blog/static/405ad2774c91e0a47bc409c08ba5dcba/3561e/Richard-Jumping.jpg 433w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 433px) 100vw, 433px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><small><i><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SsoOG6ZeyUI\">Source</a></i></small></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Tabifier Action - Convert Leading White spaces to Tabs","date":"September 08, 2020","description":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tabifier-action/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/latex-resume-website-github-action/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"GitHub Action - Create a LaTeX Resume and Website from a Single Data File"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/GSoC20-Proposal/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"GSoC 2020 Proposal - INCF"}}}}}